co.cask.coopr.common.zookeeper.lib

Class ZKMap<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • co.cask.coopr.common.zookeeper.lib.ZKMap<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - Type of object to keep in the map values.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Map<String,T>

    public class ZKMap<T>
extends Object
implements Map<String,T>
    Implementation of Map backed by Zookeeper. NOTE: it is not thread-safe and not multi-process safe. Consider using ZKInterProcessReentrantLock to guard against changes by other processes if needed.
